caption.text:
Here’s how to make Instagram show your content to the right audience:

1️⃣ More keywords

Your caption has to be more than 1-2 words.

Ideally you want to put as many keywords as possible in your caption to make an interesting, valuable or entertaining content out of them. So more people will read it and engage with your reel.

2️⃣ Topics

There is a feature on Instagram called “Topics”. You switch it on before posting a reel and select what niches you want to target with your reel

3️⃣ SEO Account optimisation

Add keywords to your username or name of your account to make yourself searcheable on the platform and let Instagram know who is your target audience

Example:
Anthony | Online Fitness Coach
Mike | Affiliate marketing guru
Jessica | Social media strategy

Follow me for daily Instagram tips ✅
